OL,3,CPolice officer killed on duty was
OL,4,Cclosing road when she was hit by car
OL,6,FA 19-year-old police officer who died
OL,7,Fafter she was hit by a car while on
OL,8,Fduty was closing a road following a
OL,9,Fprevious collision, a coroner said.
OL,11,FAn inquest has opened into the death
OL,12,Fof police constable Jess Turnbull, who
OL,13,Fsuffered "catastrophic injuries" in
OL,14,Fthe incident in Northumberland on
OL,15,FMonday 8 June.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/6
