CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1783521459
OL,3,CPolice officer killed on duty was
OL,4,Cclosing road when she was hit by car
OL,6,FThe young officer's parents, Janice
OL,7,Fand Andy ` himself a former police
OL,8,Fofficer ` attended the brief hearing
OL,9,Fheld by Coroner Andrew Hetherington at
OL,10,FNorthumberland Coroner's Court in
OL,11,FMorpeth.
OL,13,FThe coroner outlined the circumstances
OL,14,Fof her death, saying that Pc Turnbull
OL,15,Fand a colleague were sent to an
OL,16,Fearlier two-vehicle collision on the
OL,17,FA189 near Cramlington, at 11.11pm on 8
OL,18,FJune.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1783521459
OL,3,CPolice officer killed on duty was
OL,4,Cclosing road when she was hit by car
OL,6,FMr Hetherington said Pc Turnbull had
OL,7,Fgot out of the marked police vehicle
OL,8,Fand was implementing a road closure at
OL,9,Faround 11.34pm.
OL,11,FShe was standing in the carriageway
OL,12,Fnear the front of her vehicle when
OL,13,Fanother motorist collided with the
OL,14,Fparked police car, "resulting in Jess
OL,15,Fbeing hit", the coroner said.
OL,17,FPolice and paramedics treated her at
OL,18,Fthe scene and she was taken to the
OL,19,FRoyal Victoria Infirmary, Newcastle,
OL,20,Fwhere she died on Wednesday 10 June.
OL,26,@vD@TOUwD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/6
