OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1783521459
OL,3,CPolice officer killed on duty was
OL,4,Cclosing road when she was hit by car
OL,6,FMr Hetherington said a post-mortem
OL,7,Fexamination has been carried out.
OL,9,FPolice investigations are continuing
OL,10,Finto what happened that night, the
OL,11,Fcoroner said.
OL,13,FHe adjourned the full inquest hearing
OL,14,Fto 11 January but said that may change.
OL,16,FNorthumbria Police previously said
OL,17,Fthat a 73-year-old Mercedes driver was
OL,18,Farrested on suspicion of causing death
OL,19,Fby dangerous driving and has been
OL,20,Fbailed.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
