FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1783521459
OL,3,CPolice officer killed on duty was
OL,4,Cclosing road when she was hit by car
OL,6,FPc Turnbull had only joined the force
OL,7,Fin September.
OL,9,FIn a tribute released after her death,
OL,10,Fher parents said: "One of Jess's
OL,11,Fproudest achievements was becoming a
OL,12,Fpolice officer.
OL,14,F"She absolutely loved serving her
OL,15,Fcommunity and was incredibly proud to
OL,16,Fwear the uniform.
OL,26,@rD@SOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/6
