OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,393,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F392A1783521459
OL,3,CPolice officer killed on duty was
OL,4,Cclosing road when she was hit by car
OL,6,F"Following in the footsteps of her
OL,7,Fdad, Andy, was something she had
OL,8,Falways dreamed of doing, and seeing
OL,9,Fher achieve that ambition filled us
OL,10,Fboth with immense pride.
OL,12,F"Policing was not just a job to Jess,
OL,13,Fit was a calling.
OL,15,F"She cared deeply about helping people
OL,16,Fand making a difference, and she
OL,17,Fapproached every day with enthusiasm,
OL,18,Fcompassion and professionalism."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUwD@AOUzD@`O]
